            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市｜港股全日升82點  AI相關股飆  全周恒指跌107點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股全日升82點，新股狂飆，人工智能及特專科技股上揚，黃金股造好，午後個別內需股跑上，光伏股捱沽，金融股窄幅偏軟。一周計恒指先升後跌，仍累跌逾百點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數全日報26231，升82點或0.32%，今早開報26272點，升123點或0.47% ; 一度見26299，升150點或0.57%，為全日高位，其後反覆向下，最低見26114，跌35點或0.13%，為全日低位，午後不超過上午波幅。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 巴士的報記者攝</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"智譜與MiniMax的上市衝刺，成為觀察產業走向的風向標。\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/12/20251227_blog_source_web_blog4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"智譜與MiniMax的上市衝刺，成為觀察產業走向的風向標。\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/12/20251227_blog_source_web_blog4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">智譜與MiniMax的上市衝刺，成為觀察產業走向的風向標。</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"公司官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/XTALPI_02228_source-web_1200-1.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"公司官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/XTALPI_02228_source-web_1200-1.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">公司官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230718-140331_長和00001-中國屈臣氏上海正大廣場分店_source-web_1200.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230718-140331_長和00001-中國屈臣氏上海正大廣場分店_source-web_1200.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">資料圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 巴士的報記者攝</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"智譜與MiniMax的上市衝刺，成為觀察產業走向的風向標。\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/12/20251227_blog_source_web_blog4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">智譜與MiniMax的上市衝刺，成為觀察產業走向的風向標。</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"公司官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/XTALPI_02228_source-web_1200-1.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">公司官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230718-140331_長和00001-中國屈臣氏上海正大廣場分店_source-web_1200.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">資料圖片</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數全日報5687，升8點0.15%，今早開升21點或0.38%，報5699。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數全日報9048，升9點或0.1%，今早開升31點或0.35%報9070點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交2451.3億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">一周計恒指跌107點或0.41% ; 科指累跌49點或0.85% ; 國指累跌120點或1.31%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指全日升100點或0.38%，報26241，高水9點; 科指期貨升11點或0.19%，報5702點，高水15點 ; 國指期貨升20點或0.22%，報9057，高水8點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">三新股首掛狂飆，AI六小虎Minimax(00100)首掛，午後升幅擴大，全日飛升109.09%，報345元，1手20股不計手續費賺3600元 ; 瑞博生物(06938)升41.63%，報82.1元，每手200股賺4826元 ; 金潯資源(03636)升26%，報37.8元，每手賺1560元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"智譜與MiniMax的上市衝刺，成為觀察產業走向的風向標。\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/12/20251227_blog_source_web_blog4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"智譜與MiniMax的上市衝刺，成為觀察產業走向的風向標。\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/12/20251227_blog_source_web_blog4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">智譜與MiniMax的上市衝刺，成為觀察產業走向的風向標。</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)全日升2.74%，報146.5元，成交居首，推升恒指51點 ; 阿里健康(00241)升4.72%，報5.77元 ; 快手(01024)升3.89%，報74.7元 ; 京東(09618)升2.59%，報114.6元 ; 騰訊(00700)報611元，跌0.81% ; 美團(03690)跌2.48%，報98.5元，推低恒指22點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藍思科技(06613)揚9.01%，報28.8元 ; 特專科技股晶泰控股(02228)午後飆，全日升10.49%，報12.54元，成交俱入20大。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"公司官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/XTALPI_02228_source-web_1200-1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"公司官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/XTALPI_02228_source-web_1200-1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">公司官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內需股午後跑贏，康師傅(00322)收升4.02%，報11.91元，為表現最佳藍籌股; 恆安國際(01044)升0.44%，報27.26元 ; 海爾智家(06690)升1.09%，報26元。安踏(02020)傳收購PUMA，收跌1.47%，報80.3元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">黃金相關股升，摩根士丹利料金價今年見4800美元，紫金(02899)升2.85%，報38.26元 ; 老鋪黃金(06181)升5.52%，報659元 ; 山東黃金(01787)揚6.12%，報39.9元 ; 招金礦業(01818)升4.1%，報35.58元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">光伏股跌，信義光能(00968)跌3.72%，報3.11元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 協鑫科技(03800)瀉7.9%，報1.05元 ; 新特能源(01799)挫8.49%，報6.8元，內地6 大光伏龍頭被約談，當局令不得約定產能及售價，摩通指最差情況為無序內捲。風電股金風科技(02128)升3.41%，報16.67元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230718-140331_長和00001-中國屈臣氏上海正大廣場分店_source-web_1200.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230718-140331_長和00001-中國屈臣氏上海正大廣場分店_source-web_1200.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">長和傳委託高盛及瑞銀安排屈臣氏港、英兩地上市，料今年掛牌，長和升3.72%，報57.15元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生(00011)私有化議案通過，升0.39%，報154.5元，為1個月高 ; 滙控(00005)升0.4%，報124.8元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15570026-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e5%8d%8782%e9%bb%9e-ai%e7%9b%b8%e9%97%9c%e8%82%a1%e9%a3%86-%e5%85%a8%e5%91%a8%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c107%e9%bb%9e",
